column5: Ok guys where is it we have been waiting.I have been wondering did you take out the new vessel for the test run?  Has it been slimed.Please give us some news.  Big Fish?  Little fish

The more important question is... where's your Cue-beck fish slime report Big Boy???.. or can you only catch fish in Ontario???   I know... I know... you wanna know where my 'Bama fish slime report is, truth to be known.. I've been sidelined with a sprained Tallywhacker!!!... I can send you the full res pics if you'd like...

Well I've been busy getting it inspected and licenced, all the gov't gobbledegook to make it legal.  She's good to go now, but unfortunately Paul was on call last weekend so we couldn't go.  We made it out one day for a few hours to give her a test run.  T'was heaven  This weekend, slimer city hopefully.  Joey
Paul, it's okay, you can pm me your OOS PB lunge pic dude.  Nobody needs to know!
Have ya got a cast on it now? That oughta get ya some looks from the distaff side.  JF
